5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:18,800
But beware!

6
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:20,800
Not all fevers are helpful.

7
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:25,200
Fever can be a double-edged sword—it's crucial to monitor its intensity.

